DESCRIPTION:All support acts are subject to change without notice. There ar
	e no refunds or exchanges. There is no re-entry into the venue once exited
	. All patrons require a ticket\, regardless of age. Including babies in ar
	ms. Lumen Field/WAMU Theater is not responsible for third party ticket pur
	chases. There is an overall four ticket limit for this event. Anyone found
	 purchasing above the set ticket limit may have partially or their entire 
	refund cancelled. WAMU Theater has a clear bag policy\, please see our web
