	l JamCome out and join Washed in Black as they take you back to the day wh
	en flannel was king From the live vibe of the music\, to the energetic per
	formance...... The only thing better are the boys in Pearl Jam themselves!
	 JAR OF FLIES (the ultimate AIC experience) is a collection of top Seattle
	 musicians with a passion for honoring Alice in Chains. This band brings a
	n authentic and powerful sonic experience!\nThis event is 21 and over. Any
